      <title>SBM 通过增加生产船来推动巴西石油公司的石油增长</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-09-11/sbm-fuels-petrobras-s-oil-growth-with-more-production-vessels</link>
      <description><![CDATA[SBM Offshore NV 有两艘大型油船驶往巴西，目前正等待巴西石油公司对类似船只进行招标，以帮助加速拉丁美洲最大产油国的增长。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-09-11/sbm-fuels-petrobras-s-oil-growth-with-more-production-vessels</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 11 Sep 2024 15:52:12 GMT</pubDate>
